team.description:
Google is known all around the world for providing many services. For most people, they are services that just work, but not for engineers. Engineers see much more: APIs, scalability issues, complex technology stacks. And that's what GDG is about.

GDG Sydney is an open community organised by enthusiastic volunteers. Created to share experiences around Google tech, develop a network of peers and having some fun.
